OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice confirmed
OL,7,Ffunding for the Swansea Women's
OL,8,FResidential Centre was reprioritised
OL,9,Fin 2022/23.
OL,11,FThe Welsh Government says it shares
OL,12,Fconcerns about the delay of the
OL,13,FSwansea Women's Residential Centre,
OL,14,Fwhich is vital to making a distinctly
OL,15,FWelsh, trauma-informed approach to
OL,16,Fwomen's justice.
OL,18,FThere are no dedicated female-only
OL,19,Fprisons in Wales.
