OL,6,FDanielle John runs a project which
OL,7,Fhelps women who have had contact with
OL,8,Fthe criminal justice system. The 44-
OL,9,Fyear-old from Swansea spent 20 years
OL,10,Fin and out of prison for low-level
OL,11,Fcrimes.
OL,13,F"I had a very chaotic childhood," she
OL,14,Ftold ITV Wales.
OL,16,F"Something happened to me when I was
OL,17,F14, and it splintered my family, and I
OL,18,Flived on my own. I was groomed into
OL,19,Fcriminal exploitation at a young age,
OL,20,Fand I ended up in prison by the time I
OL,21,Fwas 16.
