OL,6,F"After that, I fell into a cycle of
OL,7,Faddiction, and I was in and out, over
OL,8,Fa 20-year period."
OL,10,FMs John says women in Wales who are
OL,11,Fsent to prison are being let down,
OL,12,Fwith very little support to stop them
OL,13,Freoffending. She says it's
OL,14,Fdisappointing that the residential
OL,15,Fcentre in Swansea has been held up.
