OL,6,F"When you're on short sentences, you
OL,7,Fdon't get that support, you're not in
OL,8,Fthere long enough to build a
OL,9,Frelationship with a key worker so they
OL,10,Fcan get that support in place when you
OL,11,Fcome back to Wales.
OL,13,F"So you're released, usually with just
OL,14,Fan appointment for your probation, and
OL,15,Fnothing else is in place. So
