OL,6,FDennise Avery lives near the proposed
OL,7,Fsite. She told ITV Wales she is
OL,8,Fsupportive of the need for a female-
OL,9,Ffocused rehabilitation scheme, but a
OL,10,Fbetter site is needed to protect
OL,11,Fvulnerable women and local residents.
OL,13,F"It's a worry, for local people," she
OL,14,Fsaid. "We do understand that women
OL,15,Fneed help, but there are other ways of
OL,16,Fhelping them without placing them in a
OL,17,Fresidential area, where there are a
OL,18,Flot of families around."
