OL,6,FCurrently, there are no dedicated
OL,7,Ffemale-only prisons in Wales. Women
OL,8,Ffrom South Wales who enter the
OL,9,Fcriminal justice system are sent to
OL,10,FHMP Eastwood Park in Gloucestershire,
OL,11,Fa four-hour commute from Swansea on
OL,12,Fpublic transport.
OL,14,FFigures from a 2018 Cardiff University
OL,15,Fstudy showed the average distance from
OL,16,Fhome for a Welsh female prisoner was
OL,17,F101 miles, compared to 53 miles for a
OL,18,FWelsh adult male prisoner.
